ATTRIBUTION FOR THIRD-PARTY MATERIAL

This project references and builds upon several third-party sources. The
CC BY-SA license applies to the original content and analysis in this
repository. Referenced source materials remain the property of their
respective rights holders:

  - Goethe-Institut Wortlisten (A1, A2, B1, DTZ): © Goethe-Institut
    and ÖSD. Used as a CEFR-level filter and vocabulary reference.
    https://www.goethe.de/

  - "Madrigal's Magic Key to German" by Margarita Madrigal and Ursula
    Meyer (Doubleday, 1966): cited as pedagogical inspiration.

  - Duden online dictionary: referenced for validation of spelling,
    gender, meaning, and usage notes. https://www.duden.de/

  - DWDS (Digitales Wörterbuch der deutschen Sprache): referenced for
    lemma and frequency data. https://www.dwds.de/

Example sentences in this repository are original to this project.
